cu.explanation_en: Setting the S1U port to 0 is out of range for valid port numbers and will cause socket binding failure, preventing S1U interface communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator server port to 0 is out of range for valid port numbers and will cause connection failure to the RF simulator.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RF 模擬器伺服器端口設定為 0 超出有效端口號範圍，會導致與 RF 模擬器的連接失敗。
